      <title>零售商 99 Cents Only 申请破产并计划关闭</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/retailer-99-cents-only-files-bankruptcy-plans-shut-down-2024-04-08/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[廉价零售商 99 Cents Only 周日在特拉华州根据《破产法》第 11 章申请破产保护，称其打算关闭其在美国的所有 371 家商店，并出售其房地产和剩余库存。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/retailer-99-cents-only-files-bankruptcy-plans-shut-down-2024-04-08/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 18:03:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
